comment: Thompson (CLE) sets the screen on George (IND) and gives him the opportunity to avoid the contact.
Hill (IND) makes contact with James' (CLE) arm that affects his layup attempt.
Allen (IND) sets the screen on Dellavedova (CLE) and gives him the opportunity to avoid the contact.
Thompson (CLE) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Hill's (IND) driving layup attempt.
Dellavedova (CLE) does not obtain legal guarding position as he is still moving to his right when he makes contact with Ellis (IND).
Hill (IND) sets the screen on James (CLE) and gives him the opportunity to avoid the contact.
George (IND) commits a take foul on James (CLE).
Thompson (CLE) clamps Hill's (IND) arm and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the shot by Budinger (IND) occured after the game clock had expired was upheld. NOTE: Due to an injury, the game was officiated by two referees from the 2:05 mark in the 3rd quarter until the end of the game.
